              "posName": "死之羽",
              "position": "死之羽",
              "title": "裁斷的翎羽"
            },
            "sands_of_eon": {
              "desc": "<p>暗金光澤的古老日晷，似乎在訴說著沙漠的舊日。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/08/26/7998136/8842156fb124596d6a0d7aa56f8483e0_8397128410201599574.png",
